Downloading Super CSV

* Prerequisites

      [Java 1.5+] Super CSV is compiled for Java 1.5

* Maven users

  If you are using Maven, simply copy the following dependency into your pom.xml file. 
  
+-------------------------------------+
<dependency>
    <groupId>${project.groupId}</groupId>
    <artifactId>super-csv</artifactId>
    <version>${project.version}</version>
</dependency>
+-------------------------------------+

  The artifact is hosted at {{{http://search.maven.org}Maven Central}}, and is standalone (no dependencies).
  
* Everyone else

  You can download the latest distribution zip file from {{{https://sourceforge.net/projects/supercsv/files/latest/download?source=files}SourceForge}}, 
  which contains:

*------------------------------------------------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------+
 <<File>>                                              || Description                                                           
*------------------------------------------------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------+
  super-csv-${project.version}.jar                     | Super CSV ${project.version} (compiled classes only)                 
*------------------------------------------------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------+
  super-csv-${project.version}-sources.jar             | The Java source code                                                 
*------------------------------------------------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------+
  super-csv-${project.version}-javadoc.jar             | The Javadoc documentation. Can be integrated with your favourite IDE 
*------------------------------------------------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------+